description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene ("Bacillus brevis" Lustig 1890; "Flavobacterium brevis" (sic) (Lustig 1890) Bergey et al. 1923; Bacillus canalis parvus; Bacillus canicolis brevis; Bacterium breve; Bacterium canale; Bacterium canalis parvus; Empedobacter breve; Flavobacterium breve; Pseudobacterium brevis.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
